_lazyReverse.js

 
var LazyWrapper = require('./_LazyWrapper');

Reverses the direction of lazy iteration.

 
function lazyReverse() {
  if (this.__filtered__) {
    var result = new LazyWrapper(this);
    result.__dir__ = -1;
    result.__filtered__ = true;
  } else {
    result = this.clone();
    result.__dir__ *= -1;
  }
  return result;
}

module.exports = lazyReverse;
